                    <body>
                              <pb n="1"/>
                              <p rend="align(right)">
                                        <add>Hebrew</add>
                                        <placeName>New York</placeName>
                                        <date>April 4<hi rend="sup">th</hi> 5614</date>
                              </p>
                              <p>
                                        <add>Hebrew</add>
                              </p>
                              <p>
                                        <persName role="author">Michael Light</persName>
                              </p>
                              <p rend="indent(1)">
                                        <placeName>188 Ludlow Street</placeName>
                              </p>
                              <pb n="2"/>
                              <p rend="align(right)"><placeName>New York</placeName>, <date>April 4,
                                                  1854</date>.</p>
                              <p rend="align(right)">
                                        <date>6<hi rend="sup">th</hi> of Nissan</date>
                              </p>
                              <p>Peace and all good forever, very honored sir:</p>
                              <p rend="indent(1)">I have received your honored letter of yesterday's
                                        date,<lb/> and I must reply to you that your conclusion was
                                        quite correct. I have,<lb/> in fact, forgotten to enclose
                                        the money, and when I returned from the<lb/>
                                        <sic>postoffice</sic>, I noticed it. I have sent four
                                        Haggadoth with English<lb/> translation to <placeName>St.
                                                  Louis</placeName>.</p>
                              <p rend="indent(1)">With wishes for a happy holiday, I sign</p>
                              <p rend="indent(3)">Respectfully,</p>
                              <p rend="indent(4)">Your most devoted,</p>
                              <p rend="indent(5)"><persName role="author">Michael</persName>, son of
                                                  <persName>Rabbi Abraham</persName></p>
                              <p rend="indent(8)">
                                        <persName>Uri</persName>
                              </p>
                              <p rend="indent(5)">
                                        <persName role="author">Michael Light</persName>
                              </p>
                              <p rend="indent(6)">
                                        <placeName>188 Ludlow Street</placeName>
                              </p>
